# Build your Smart Hospital with care.ai
The World’s Most Advanced Smart Care Facility Platform

Our fundamental pursuit is to help healthcare move beyond legacy single-point solutions by building an Ambiently-Aware Artificial Intelligence Platform that is tirelessly committed to supporting care teams and patients every hour of every day.

## Empower Your Smart Care Team
### AI-Assisted Virtual Nursing Smart from The Start
Our fundamental pursuit is to help healthcare move beyond legacy single-point solutions by building an Ambiently-Aware Artificial Intelligence Platform that is tirelessly committed to supporting care teams and patients every hour of every day.

We build category-leading AI and Ambient Intelligent Sensors to power next-generation Virtual Care Solutions for more timely moments of compassionate care with a human touch.

[Learn more about Smart Care Teams](#)

## The End of the EMR Keyboard Age
Clinicians spend time with patients, not data entry.

## Smart Patient Rooms Always On. Always Aware.
care.ai Always-Aware Ambient Sensors make patient rooms “self-aware,” empowering physicians, nurses and staff to be more proactive, helping them to identify potential risks.

[Learn more about Smart Patient Rooms](#)

## Self-Aware Smart Care Spaces
care.ai smart patient rooms, emergency rooms and operating rooms use a combination of sensors, automated systems, and artificial intelligence to create a more responsive and personalized healthcare environment.

### AI-Assisted Virtual Care
care.ai sensors include high-resolution cameras and work with existing TV displays so that patients have more convenient access to their Smart Care Team both bed-side or virtual.

### Generative AI Caring Co-pilot
care.ai integration with generative AI and the patient’s electronic health records helps ensure care is aligned with established workflows and protocols, providing care team members with workflow insights and support.

## Edge-to-Cloud Ambient Sensors Built to Scale
care.ai ambient sensor arrays securely support patient well-being and provide real-time AI guidance while connecting all hospital departments to enable proactive support and communication.

[Learn more about Always-Aware Ambient Sensors](#)

### Easy IoT Installation
Ultra-secure and built with healthcare-grade materials, care.ai sensors are plug-and-play, work with existing network connections and TVs and are easy to deploy and provision.

### Low Latency + Low Network Load
care.ai’s Always-Aware Sensors combine local AI inferencing, virtual care support, and ambient monitoring on a powerful edge compute neural network, keeping local response times fast with low latency and low network load.

### AI Federated Learning
care.ai sensors are always learning and always improving, securely sharing that learning from one sensor to the next. Many networked AI brains act together as one to serve and protect clinicians and patients.

## AI-Assisted Command Center Connects & Protects
We are building the definitive AI-Human spatial computing Smart-Care Environment, extending life and quality of life for the benefit of humankind.

[Learn more about Smart Hospital Command Center](#)

### Real-Time Awareness
Instead of latent and often erroneous information trapped in the EHR, now Smart Care Teams have real-time awareness. The Command Center automatically suggests where attention and available resources should be applied.

### Reduced Administrative Burden for Clinicians
Ambient Intelligence and AI help automate and virtualize administrative tasks, allowing more time for the bedside clinical team to work at the top of their licenses and provide more timely moments of compassionate care.

### Autonomous Improvement
Ambient Sensors and AI monitor clinical and operational workflows and coordinate care teams to ensure continual process adherence and improvement, eliminating ineffective and costly recurrent training programs.

## Smart from the Start Solutions AI-Powered Workflows for Every Care Setting
